overview: 10th Anniversary Show: Young Wolves Rising was a professional wrestling pay-per-view (PPV) event produced by the Ring of Honor (ROH) promotion, that took place on March 4, 2012 at the Hammerstein Ballroom in New York City. It was the tenth "Anniversary Show" and the first event in the 2012 ROH PPV schedule.
title: ROH: 10th Anniversary
